      "span_text": "Another approach is utilized by the support vector machine algorithm (SVM)  : This mathematical procedure is based on training samples from the Monte Carlo simulation, using the signal proportion on each PMT in the top array for a given (x, y) position, to create a base of vectors in a projected multidimensional space."
